    "The second, however, uses tags that are assigned to conference talks.",
    "Once again, a matching is carried out between the tags of interest to the user and those from the talks.",
    "Similar users are also recommended according to profile closeness, and all the recommended information is shown as a clustermap, combining recommended users, tags, talks, and papers.",
